<title>GREECE: Athens bourse approves Korasidis merger.</title>
<headline>Athens bourse approves Korasidis merger.</headline>
<dateline>ATHENS 1997-07-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Athens stock exchange approved the prospectus for the merger of electrical retailer Radio Korasidis with its subsidiary Radio Korasidis Commercial SA, it said in a statement.</p>
<p>Listed Radio Korasisids will absorb the commercial subsidiary and raise its share capital by around 305 million drachmas, issuing 3,055,900 new common registered shares.</p>
<p>Its shareholders will be offered six bonus shares per ten outstanding. --Angelos Kiosklis, Athens Newsroom +301 3311812-4</p>
